1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=Detik Aku Bertemu Kamu=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episod 3=

3
00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:19,160
Bukankah kita nak serang hendap dia?

4
00:00:19,359 --> 00:00:21,120
Kenapa tiba-tiba tukar kepada racun?

5
00:00:21,440 --> 00:00:23,039
Serang hendap pun mungkin kita tak menang.

6
00:00:23,039 --> 00:00:24,440
Guna racun lagi selamat.

7
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:26,760
Kalau aku kebal semua toksin macam mana?

8
00:00:26,760 --> 00:00:29,160
(Qian, orang suruhan Li Wan)
Kalau begitu, kita buat cara susah.

9
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:33,890
Jangan takut pada dia.

10
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:34,580
Buat saja!

11
00:00:36,719 --> 00:00:37,880
Ingat kata-kata aku, Chu Yunchang,

12
00:00:38,159 --> 00:00:39,975
ini belum habis antara kita!

13
00:00:40,119 --> 00:00:42,039
(Aduh, kenapa dia kembali?)

14
00:00:42,399 --> 00:00:43,000
(Apa-apa sajalah.)

15
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:44,350
(Aku pura-pura tak pandai berlawan.)

16
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:48,119
Qian!

17
00:00:48,119 --> 00:00:49,119
Tumbang dengan satu pukulan!

18
00:00:49,719 --> 00:00:51,359
Rupanya kau memang sorok kekuatan.

19
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:53,240
Sekejap... betul ke aku buat tadi?

20
00:00:53,719 --> 00:00:54,520
Memang betul!

21
00:00:55,960 --> 00:00:56,799
Kamu semua siapa?

22
00:00:58,240 --> 00:00:59,039
Macam mana dengan dia?

23
00:00:59,240 --> 00:01:00,880
Tak payah! Ikat dua-dua sekali!

24
00:01:05,925 --> 00:01:06,565
Yunchang?

25
00:01:10,790 --> 00:01:11,599
(Dia pergi mana?)

26
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,400
Alamak, teruklah macam ni.

27
00:01:17,719 --> 00:01:18,319
Buyu!

28
00:01:18,760 --> 00:01:20,239
Seorang gadis bernama Zhizhi baru datang.

29
00:01:20,239 --> 00:01:21,120
Perguruan Tiga Tangan

30
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:22,239
dah culik Rong dan Chang.

31
00:01:22,319 --> 00:01:23,519
Aku pun baru dapat maklumat.

32
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:24,930
Ada gerakan pelik
di pinggir barat.

33
00:01:24,959 --> 00:01:25,560
Jom.

34
00:01:25,719 --> 00:01:26,480
Aku kumpulkan orang.

35
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:27,159
Tak sempat!

36
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:32,200
Kenapa pencuri tu nak culik kau?

37
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:34,079
Mana aku tahu?

38
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:35,640
Aku pun mangsa juga.

39
00:01:36,959 --> 00:01:38,280
Mungkin mereka nak

40
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:40,359
memeras duit daripada mak cik pak cik aku.

41
00:01:40,799 --> 00:01:42,799
Sampai sekarang kau masih tak nak jujur?

42
00:01:43,359 --> 00:01:44,239
Lelaki bernama Li Wan itu

43
00:01:44,239 --> 00:01:45,879
ketua Perguruan Tiga Tangan.

44
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,799
Apa sebenarnya Perguruan Tiga Tangan tu?

45
00:01:49,799 --> 00:01:51,120
Dia datang hari jadi kau!

46
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:51,879
Berhenti berpura-pura.

47
00:01:52,519 --> 00:01:54,879
Itu cuma sebab hormat
mak cik dan pak cik aku.

48
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:55,920
Chu Yunchang,

49
00:01:56,519 --> 00:01:57,280
saudara aku

50
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:59,000
sangat serius tentang perasaannya.

51
00:01:59,230 --> 00:02:01,159
Aku harap kau bukan
main-mainkan dia.

52
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:05,040
Aku pun serius dengan perasaan aku.

53
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:08,080
Selagi dia setia pada aku,

54
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,439
aku sanggup korbankan nyawa untuk dia.

55
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:17,439
Ingatkan kau hebat tadi.

56
00:02:17,719 --> 00:02:19,159
Rupanya tak ada apa-apa pun.

57
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:21,639
Kalau aku tahu,
aku takkan susahkan Qian.

58
00:02:22,039 --> 00:02:23,840
Aku boleh jimat
seribu tael perak.

59
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:25,560
Dia kata seni bela diri kau lemah.

60
00:02:25,919 --> 00:02:26,919
Kamu ramai lawan kami.

61
00:02:26,919 --> 00:02:27,900
Tak ada maruah pun.

62
00:02:27,919 --> 00:02:28,479
Ha!

63
00:02:28,759 --> 00:02:30,199
Kau tak layak nak megah.

64
00:02:30,759 --> 00:02:31,680
Dah habis riwayat kau,

65
00:02:32,199 --> 00:02:33,479
ada kata-kata akhir?

66
00:02:34,599 --> 00:02:36,759
Kalau mak cik pak cik aku jumpa kau?

67
00:02:38,319 --> 00:02:41,080
Kau ingat aku takut
pada Raja Pencuri?

68
00:02:43,039 --> 00:02:44,159
Raja Pencuri?

69
00:02:44,479 --> 00:02:45,719
Apa kaitan pak cik kau dengan ini?

70
00:02:45,719 --> 00:02:46,919
Aku dah cakap diam, kan?

71
00:02:46,919 --> 00:02:47,840
Diam!

72
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:49,000
Kau yang diam!

73
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,210
Kau tahu tak siapa aku?

74
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:51,639
Dia betul.

75
00:02:51,639 --> 00:02:52,639
Ini tak ada kena-mengena dengan dia.

76
00:02:52,639 --> 00:02:53,879
Lepaskan dia.

77
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:56,639
Kalau tak,
padahnya kau tanggung.

78
00:02:56,639 --> 00:02:57,479
Chu Yunchang,

79
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,199
jangan besar kepala sangat.

80
00:02:59,479 --> 00:03:00,439
Sekarang,

81
00:03:00,759 --> 00:03:02,159
bukan kau yang berkuasa.

82
00:03:02,159 --> 00:03:04,270
Aku Mao Wenrong
dari Unit Risikan Gate Bureau.

83
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,879
Kalau kau bijak, lepaskan aku sekarang.

84
00:03:06,159 --> 00:03:07,479
Kau dari Gate Bureau?

85
00:03:08,319 --> 00:03:11,120
Bagus. Jadi aku ada bukti
kau bersekongkol dengan mereka.

86
00:03:12,319 --> 00:03:13,360
Dia menipu.

87
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:13,960
Mengarut.

88
00:03:14,550 --> 00:03:15,430
Ini lencana aku!

89
00:03:16,610 --> 00:03:17,879
Kau memang orang Bureau.

90
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:20,120
Kalau begitu, aku takkan lepaskan kau.

91
00:03:20,759 --> 00:03:22,840
Kamu berdua pun cantik juga.

92
00:03:24,719 --> 00:03:26,719
Jangan salahkan aku kalau jadi apa-apa nanti.

93
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:27,919
Jangan berani!

94
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,039
Rong...

95
00:03:31,330 --> 00:03:32,319
Jangan salah faham.

96
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:34,159
Aku masih tak suka kau.

97
00:03:34,479 --> 00:03:35,759
Tapi sebagai konstabel,

98
00:03:35,759 --> 00:03:36,800
aku takkan biar apa-apa jenayah

99
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:37,990
berlaku depan mata aku.

100
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,560
Kalau kau sentuh kami,

101
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:41,159
Gate Bureau akan buru kau sampai dapat.

102
00:03:42,159 --> 00:03:44,240
Berani juga kau, ya?

103
00:03:46,719 --> 00:03:47,879
Aku tahu kau nak selamatkan Rong,

104
00:03:47,879 --> 00:03:48,960
tapi kita mungkin kalah bilangan.

105
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:49,960
Itu tak penting sekarang!

106
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:52,580
Adik aku dan Chang dah lama dibawa pergi.

107
00:03:52,599 --> 00:03:53,620
Kita tak boleh lengah lagi!

108
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:02,639
Siapa tu?

109
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,439
Kepung mereka!

110
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,390
Ini wilayah Perguruan Tiga Tangan!

111
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,199
Mati!

112
00:04:11,159 --> 00:04:12,280
Buyu, rapat dengan aku.

113
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,000
Aku lindungi kau!

114
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,759
Jangan lepaskan seorang pun.

115
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:19,759
Jangan berani!

116
00:04:21,199 --> 00:04:22,560
Dengan gadis kecil secantik ini,

117
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,519
kenapa aku tak berani?

118
00:04:23,519 --> 00:04:24,260
Lari selagi boleh!

119
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,199
Aku bunuh kau!

120
00:04:32,839 --> 00:04:33,600
Ketua Li,

121
00:04:35,199 --> 00:04:36,839
cepatnya dah lupa aku?

122
00:04:40,079 --> 00:04:40,759
Li Wan,

123
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:42,720
kau khianati Pakatan Dunia Persilatan,

124
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,040
lepas tu berpaling tadah pada Lin Xin'er.

125
00:04:44,399 --> 00:04:46,279
Sekarang pula, kau memburu wanita tak bersalah.

126
00:04:46,839 --> 00:04:48,240
Jenayah kau sangat keji.

127
00:04:48,519 --> 00:04:50,290
Sebagai ketua agung
Pakatan Dunia Persilatan,

128
00:04:50,759 --> 00:04:52,160
aku akan bersihkan pakatan ini!

129
00:04:58,079 --> 00:04:59,279
Kamu tak perlukan bantuan kami.

130
00:05:00,839 --> 00:05:01,959
Apa jadi pada dia?

131
00:05:03,399 --> 00:05:04,959
Dia ditumbangkan sampai pengsan

132
00:05:05,079 --> 00:05:05,959
semasa cuba selamatkan aku.

133
00:05:06,519 --> 00:05:08,279
Nampaknya dia nak jadikan kamu hadiah

134
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:10,800
untuk sertai Kumpulan Pencuri Selatan.

135
00:05:11,519 --> 00:05:12,199
Chang,

136
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:14,519
Mao Wenrong ialah pegawai kerajaan.

137
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:16,560
Kalau dia sedar dan bersuara,

138
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,780
macam mana kamu nak jelaskan?

139
00:05:18,079 --> 00:05:19,240
Dia tak nampak apa-apa.

140
00:05:21,199 --> 00:05:23,040
Mao Wenrong mungkin susah diurus,

141
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,279
tapi dia cuba lindungi aku.

142
00:05:24,279 --> 00:05:25,279
Kita tak boleh sakiti dia.

143
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:28,959
Kita jangan tunggu di sini.

144
00:05:28,959 --> 00:05:29,879
Jom balik.

145
00:05:29,959 --> 00:05:30,720
Aku tolong dukung dia.

146
00:05:31,759 --> 00:05:33,959
Puak Tiga Tangan takkan berkumpul tanpa sebab.

147
00:05:34,839 --> 00:05:36,079
Mereka mungkin timbulkan masalah lagi.

148
00:05:36,079 --> 00:05:36,990
Aku kena periksa.

149
00:05:37,839 --> 00:05:38,519
Tak perlu.

150
00:05:38,879 --> 00:05:39,920
Masa kami datang tadi,

151
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,319
kami dah maklumkan Biro Gate.

152
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,920
Jadi Buyu pun akan datang?

153
00:05:43,519 --> 00:05:44,879
Aku dan Rong belum boleh pergi lagi.

154
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,879
Jadi Buyu memang dengan Biro Gate.

155
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,040
Kenapa kamu tipu aku?

156
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:50,319
Sekarang bukan masa nak selesaikan itu.

157
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:51,519
Kita gerak dulu.

158
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:57,959
Aku tak beritahu kamu tentang latar Buyu

159
00:05:58,199 --> 00:05:59,839
sebab aku tak nak kamu risau.

160
00:06:00,439 --> 00:06:01,839
Kamu semua pergi dulu.

161
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,480
Dia takkan dapat tangkap aku.

162
00:06:03,879 --> 00:06:06,480
Kamu dan dia diculik tanpa sebab pula macam mana?

163
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,959
Dah fikir alasan untuk Mao Buyu?

164
00:06:08,959 --> 00:06:10,610
Aku akan kata sebab kawan jahat kamu.

165
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,079
Mereka nampak kami kaya,

166
00:06:12,079 --> 00:06:12,920
jadi mereka culik aku.

167
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,519
Budak kurang ajar.

168
00:06:38,319 --> 00:06:39,560
Jade Squirrel.

169
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,920
Memang kamu rupanya.

170
00:06:41,070 --> 00:06:42,600
Sebagai ketua agung dunia persilatan,

171
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:45,360
kamu hasut Puak Tiga Tangan culik adik dan tunang aku.

172
00:06:45,519 --> 00:06:46,639
Apa sebenarnya yang kamu mahu?

173
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:47,959
Mereka bukan...

174
00:06:57,959 --> 00:06:59,439
Itu takkan halang aku tangkap kamu.

175
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,319
Jade Squirrel!

176
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,279
Gao Shun!

177
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,480
Hentikan kejaran!

178
00:07:10,100 --> 00:07:11,680
Selamatkan adik aku dan Chang dulu.

179
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,519
Dia cedera. Dia takkan jauh.

180
00:07:25,439 --> 00:07:26,120
Yunchang!

181
00:07:27,519 --> 00:07:29,279
Yunchang! Chu Yunchang!

182
00:07:29,279 --> 00:07:31,480
Tolong! Sesiapa, tolong!

183
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:33,160
Cepat, tolong!

184
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:34,759
Tolong!

185
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:35,639
Chang!

186
00:07:35,639 --> 00:07:36,199
Buyu!

187
00:07:36,839 --> 00:07:37,439
Chang!

188
00:07:39,319 --> 00:07:40,160
Siapa buat begini?

189
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,800
Mesti Li Wan.

190
00:07:42,079 --> 00:07:43,199
Dia cuba serang dan mencabul aku.

191
00:07:43,279 --> 00:07:44,120
Yunchang, dia...

192
00:07:44,759 --> 00:07:45,360
Ini salah aku.

193
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:47,759
Yunchang cedera masa selamatkan aku.

194
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,839
Dia cedera teruk.

195
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,360
Kita kena panggil tabib sekarang.

196
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:59,187
(Awan Meninggi)

197
00:08:05,439 --> 00:08:06,079
Buyu,

198
00:08:06,519 --> 00:08:07,439
semuanya salah aku.

199
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:08,759
Sebagai konstabel,

200
00:08:08,759 --> 00:08:10,439
aku gagal lindungi Chu Yunchang.

201
00:08:10,839 --> 00:08:12,199
Sebaliknya, dia terima pukulan yang kuat

202
00:08:12,199 --> 00:08:13,480
semata-mata nak selamatkan nyawa aku.

203
00:08:13,839 --> 00:08:15,079
Kita kena buat apa saja yang termampu

204
00:08:15,079 --> 00:08:16,279
untuk bantu dia pulih.

205
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:18,639
Tabib terbaik di bandar ini

206
00:08:18,639 --> 00:08:20,040
dah pun rawat Chang.

207
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,120
Dia akan selamat.

208
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:26,639
Chang!

209
00:08:26,639 --> 00:08:27,920
Puan Mei, Tuan Mei.

210
00:08:28,319 --> 00:08:29,319
Macam mana dia?

211
00:08:29,879 --> 00:08:31,079
Tabib masih bersama dia.

212
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,159
Ini salah kamu!

213
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:34,159
Kamu yang buat dia jadi begini!

214
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:35,720
Jangan salahkan Buyu. Ini salah aku.

215
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,399
Yunchang selamatkan aku...

216
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:46,200
Chang kami membesar tanpa calar sedikit pun.

217
00:08:47,039 --> 00:08:48,480
Tapi sejak hari dia jumpa kamu berdua,

218
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:50,159
yang ada cuma masalah.

219
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,080
Keluar!

220
00:08:52,639 --> 00:08:53,759
Kamu tak dialu-alukan di sini!

221
00:08:54,799 --> 00:08:55,799
Kami memang bersalah.

222
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,519
Tapi aku takkan pergi

223
00:08:58,679 --> 00:09:00,799
sampai dia sedar dan aku tahu dia tak apa.

224
00:09:02,919 --> 00:09:03,639
Buyu,

225
00:09:04,039 --> 00:09:05,799
mungkin kita balik dulu buat masa ini.

226
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:08,279
Kita datang semula bila mereka dah tenang.

227
00:09:08,679 --> 00:09:10,559
Aku ingat di rumah ada herba bermutu.

228
00:09:10,559 --> 00:09:12,679
Jom ambilkan untuk Cik Chu.

229
00:09:12,679 --> 00:09:14,320
Kami tak mahu herba kamu!

230
00:09:18,639 --> 00:09:20,200
Biar mereka semua masuk.

231
00:09:20,639 --> 00:09:21,559
Kamu cedera teruk.

232
00:09:21,559 --> 00:09:23,000
Lebih baik jangan bercakap.

233
00:09:23,559 --> 00:09:24,279
Masuk.

234
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:33,679
Chang...

235
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:35,879
Aku tak apa-apa.

236
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:39,120
Kecederaan perut Cik Chu sangat serius.

237
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,320
Dia kehilangan banyak darah.

238
00:09:40,679 --> 00:09:41,559
Untuk beberapa hari ini,

239
00:09:41,559 --> 00:09:43,120
kamu mesti jaga pemakanannya dengan teliti

240
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,519
dan pastikan dia banyak berehat.

241
00:09:44,679 --> 00:09:46,559
Dia tak boleh paksa diri.

242
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:49,000
Lukanya agak dalam.

243
00:09:49,399 --> 00:09:51,000
Walau dah aku jahitkan,

244
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:53,639
mungkin akan tinggalkan parut.

245
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,360
Terima kasih, tuan.

246
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:59,480
Zhizhi, ikut tabib ambil herba.

247
00:10:01,159 --> 00:10:02,039
Ikut saya.

248
00:10:11,639 --> 00:10:12,480
Masih sakit lagi?

249
00:10:15,559 --> 00:10:16,440
Aku tak apa-apa.

250
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,320
Jangan risau.

251
00:10:18,679 --> 00:10:19,320
Chang,

252
00:10:19,559 --> 00:10:20,919
kamu alami kecederaan yang teruk.

253
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,440
Kamu kena jimat tenaga.

254
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:28,080
Chang, kecederaan kamu serius.

255
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,559
Lebih baik kamu berehat sekarang.

256
00:10:30,519 --> 00:10:32,480
Aku akan ambilkan herba berharga untuk kamu.

257
00:10:43,919 --> 00:10:44,559
Yunchang,

258
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,279
Aku silap sebelum ini.

259
00:10:46,559 --> 00:10:47,759
Aku tak patut syak kamu.

260
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,120
Tumpu pada pemulihan kamu.

261
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:50,639
Kami akan datang lawat kamu tak lama lagi.

262
00:10:54,399 --> 00:10:55,159
Jom.

263
00:11:00,879 --> 00:11:01,399
Chang,

264
00:11:01,879 --> 00:11:03,399
jangan berlagak hero hanya sebab

265
00:11:03,399 --> 00:11:04,399
kau handal bertarung.

266
00:11:04,639 --> 00:11:06,399
Kau hampir kehilangan nyawa

267
00:11:06,519 --> 00:11:08,000
disebabkan Mao Buyu.

268
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:12,200
Sekurang-kurangnya hasilnya baik.

269
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:15,639
Rong dah terima aku sekarang.

270
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:18,879
Tapi aku tak setuju!

271
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:21,000
Seluruh keluarga mereka
dengan Biro Pintu.

272
00:11:21,310 --> 00:11:23,399
Lagipun Mao Buyu puncanya
kau jadi begini.

273
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:24,960
Aku takkan setuju perkahwinan ini.

274
00:11:28,559 --> 00:11:29,240
Chang,

275
00:11:29,639 --> 00:11:30,559
berehatlah.

276
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,279
Mak cik kau cuma sedang marah.

277
00:11:32,279 --> 00:11:32,840
Betul?

278
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,000
Kau buat apa?

279
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:36,720
Jom pergi.

280
00:11:38,799 --> 00:11:39,639
Jom.

281
00:11:47,112 --> 00:11:50,387
♪Dendam dan sesal
bagai arak kuat♪

282
00:11:50,425 --> 00:11:53,300
♪Teguk habis, lepaskan semuanya♪

283
00:11:53,800 --> 00:11:59,518
♪Cawan kosong untuk cinta dan benci♪

284
00:12:00,700 --> 00:12:04,020
♪Air mata kaburkan nasib yang tak terkawal♪

285
00:12:04,150 --> 00:12:07,070
♪Mari minum sampai subuh♪

286
00:12:08,238 --> 00:12:13,478
♪Di sebalik topeng ini, aku takkan menipu♪

287
00:12:14,700 --> 00:12:17,093
♪Setiap pertemuan semula rasa macam pertama♪

288
00:12:17,093 --> 00:12:20,743
♪Senyum tersembunyi ini takkan pudar♪

289
00:12:20,812 --> 00:12:24,302
♪Satu hati, berdiri di sisimu♪

290
00:12:24,400 --> 00:12:27,375
♪Hingga ke hujung waktu♪

291
00:12:27,375 --> 00:12:30,750
♪Bulan mengukir wajahmu♪

292
00:12:30,937 --> 00:12:34,525
♪Diselubungi awan, kau penuhi hatiku♪

293
00:12:34,525 --> 00:12:40,765
♪Mencari dirimu
dan menepati janji selamanya♪

294
00:12:41,100 --> 00:12:44,315
♪Doa diam dalam jiwaku♪

295
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:48,138
♪Mendukung ikrarku di bawah bulan♪

296
00:12:48,425 --> 00:12:51,450
♪Berharap kita takkan berpisah lagi♪

297
00:12:51,450 --> 00:12:54,550
♪Menuju ke selamanya♪

298
00:12:54,550 --> 00:12:58,400
♪Bulan mengukir wajahmu♪

299
00:12:58,400 --> 00:13:01,760
♪Diselubungi awan, kau penuhi hatiku♪

300
00:13:01,950 --> 00:13:07,910
♪Mencari dirimu
dan menepati janji selamanya♪

301
00:13:08,987 --> 00:13:18,627
♪Hanya untuk bersamamu♪

